type":"phase_start","content":"狼人讨论","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"phase":"night_werewolf_discuss","phaseName":"狼人讨论","timestamp":1776790774252},{"id":8,"type":"speech","content":"首夜盲刀，大家随便聊聊目标。我建议从2、3、4里面选一个刀，看看能不能摸到神。大家觉得呢？","playerId":8,"playerName":"大军","visibility":"camp","metadata":{},"timestamp":1776790785560},{"id":9,"type":"speech","content":"同意5号，首夜没信息就盲刀2、3、4吧。我倾向于刀3号，中间位置容易出神。刀完看明天谁跳预言家再定策略。谁准备上警悍跳？","playerId":5,"playerName":"阿明","visibility":"camp","metadata":{},"timestamp":1776790788600},{"id":10,"type":"speech","content":"让5号憾跳吧，我们在警下，就2吧","playerId":1,"playerName":"aa","visibility":"camp","metadata":{},"timestamp":1776790889530},{"id":11,"type":"speech","content":"同意9号，5号上警悍跳，我警下观察。首夜盲刀2号试试水。","playerId":2,"playerName":"Claude","visibility":"camp","metadata":{},"timestamp":1776790919880},{"id":12,"type":"phase_start","content":"狼人投票","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"phase":"night_werewolf_vote","phaseName":"狼人投票","timestamp":1776790919881},{"id":13,"type":"wolf_vote_result","content":"狼人选择击杀 2号阿伟","playerId":8,"visibility":"camp","metadata":{},"voteDetails":[{"voter":"5号大军","target":"2号阿伟"},{"voter":"8号阿明","target":"2号阿伟"},{"voter":"9号aa","target":"2号阿伟"},{"voter":"12号Claude","target":"2号阿伟"}],"voteCounts":{"12":4},"timestamp":1776790943048},{"id":14,"type":"phase_start","content":"女巫技能","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"phase":"witch","phaseName":"女巫技能","timestamp":1776790943049},{"id":15,"type":"phase_start","content":"预言家查验","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"phase":"seer","phaseName":"预言家查验","timestamp":1776790945152},{"id":17,"type":"phase_start","content":"警长竞选","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"phase":"sheriff_campaign","phaseName":"警长竞选","timestamp":1776790952146},{"id":18,"type":"sheriff_candidates","content":"警上：1号阿华、5号大军、7号小娟、11号大刚 | 警下：2号阿伟、3号小云、4号阿鹏、6号小芳、8号阿明、9号aa、10号阿杰、12号Claude","visibility":"public","metadata":{"onStage":[{"id":7,"name":"阿华"},{"id":8,"name":"大军"},{"id":9,"name":"小娟"},{"id":4,"name":"大刚"}],"offStage":[{"id":12,"name":"阿伟"},{"id":6,"name":"小云"},{"id":3,"name":"阿鹏"},{"id":10,"name":"小芳"},{"id":5,"name":"阿明"},{"id":1,"name":"aa"},{"id":11,"name":"阿杰"},{"id":2,"name":"Claude"}]},"timestamp":1776790968357},{"id":19,"type":"phase_start","content":"警长竞选发言","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"phase":"sheriff_speech","phaseName":"警长竞选发言","timestamp":1776790968360},{"id":20,"type":"speech","content":"我是1号阿华，上警是为了拿警长带队。作为村民，我没有信息包袱，能客观分析发言和票型。我会用理性推理找狼，警徽也不会乱飞。选我，好人方向更清晰。","playerId":7,"playerName":"阿华","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"timestamp":1776790976323},{"id":21,"type":"speech","content":"我是真预言家！昨夜验6号小芳，金水。1号平民拿警徽毫无意义，信息权必须在真预言家手里。警徽流先7后11。6号及警下好人们，请把票投给我，我带队抓狼！","playerId":8,"playerName":"大军","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"timestamp":1776791006549},{"id":22,"type":"speech","content":"5号给我警徽流，我是好人验我必金水。1号村民抢警徽毫无意义！我上警本为诈身份，既然5号起跳，我7号村民退水，把舞台留给预言家。警下听11号和后置位发言。","playerId":9,"playerName":"小娟","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"timestamp":1776791028210},{"id":23,"type":"speech","content":"5号查验我，我是村民，验我必金水。1号平民抢警徽毫无意义，7号已退水。警徽必须给预言家带队，我也退水，不占警上位置。警下好人请投5号，我绝不拿警徽！","playerId":4,"playerName":"大刚","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"timestamp":1776791055464},{"id":24,"type":"system","content":"7号小娟 退水","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"timestamp":1776791059438},{"id":25,"type":"system","content":"11号大刚 退水","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"timestamp":1776791060210},{"id":26,"type":"system","content":"1号阿华 退水","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"timestamp":1776791070393},{"id":27,"type":"phase_start","content":"警长投票","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"phase":"sheriff_vote","phaseName":"警长投票","timestamp":1776791070395},{"id":28,"type":"sheriff_elected","content":"5号大军 当选警长","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"timestamp":1776791070396},{"id":29,"type":"phase_start","content":"公布死讯","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"phase":"day_announce","phaseName":"公布死讯","timestamp":1776791070399},{"id":30,"type":"last_words","content":"我是2号女巫阿伟！首夜狼刀信息我带走了，未能自救。5号预言家身份大概率可信，6号金水可认。毒药未用，后续女巫视角缺失，请守卫暗保神职。好人跟5号警长走，仔细分辨警徽流7、11的验人结果！","playerId":12,"playerName":"阿伟","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"timestamp":1776791093179},{"id":31,"type":"death_announce","content":"2号阿伟 死亡","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"deaths":[{"id":12,"name":"阿伟","reason":"wolf"}],"timestamp":1776791093180},{"id":32,"type":"phase_start","content":"白天讨论","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"phase":"day_discuss","phaseName":"白天讨论","timestamp":1776791093183},{"id":33,"type":"system","content":"警长指定从 3号小云 开始发言","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"timestamp":1776791120112}],"sheriff":8,"couples":null,"playerCount":12,"preset":{"id":"12-guard-cupid","name":"12人守丘局","description":"含守卫丘比特，有情侣第三方","playerCount":12,"roles":["werewolf","werewolf","werewolf","werewolf","seer","witch","guard","hunter","cupid","villager","villager","villager"],"ruleDescriptions":["女巫仅首夜可自救","守卫不可连守","同守同救则死亡","猎人被毒不能开枪","首夜和白天死亡有遗言，后续夜晚死亡无遗言","情侣一方死亡另一方殉情","狼人屠边获胜；好人需清理所有狼人","人狼恋时，好人/狼人都需清理情侣+丘比特才能获胜","人狼恋胜利：情侣+丘比特存活，其他人全死"]},"dayCount":1,"winner":null,"gameOverInfo":null,"speechQueue":[6,3,10,9,5,1,11,4,2,7,8],"currentSpeakerId":6,"sheriffAssignOrder":6,"self":{"id":1,"name":"aa","role":{"id":"werewolf","name":"狼人","camp":"wolf","type":"wolf","skills":{"explode":{"type":"instant","availablePhases":["sheriff_campaign","sheriff_speech","sheriff_vote","day_discuss","day_vote"]}},"state":{}},"state":{},"alive":true,"isCouple":false,"couplePartner":null,"lastGuardTarget":null,"seerChecks":[]},"pendingAction":null}
