type":"phase_start","content":"狼人讨论","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"phase":"night_werewolf_discuss","phaseName":"狼人讨论","timestamp":1776790774252},{"id":8,"type":"speech","content":"首夜盲刀，大家随便聊聊目标。我建议从2、3、4里面选一个刀，看看能不能摸到神。大家觉得呢？","playerId":8,"playerName":"大军","visibility":"camp","metadata":{},"timestamp":1776790785560},{"id":9,"type":"speech","content":"同意5号，首夜没信息就盲刀2、3、4吧。我倾向于刀3号，中间位置容易出神。刀完看明天谁跳预言家再定策略。谁准备上警悍跳？","playerId":5,"playerName":"阿明","visibility":"camp","metadata":{},"timestamp":1776790788600},{"id":10,"type":"speech","content":"让5号憾跳吧，我们在警下，就2吧","playerId":1,"playerName":"aa","visibility":"camp","metadata":{},"timestamp":1776790889530},{"id":11,"type":"speech","content":"同意9号，5号上警悍跳，我警下观察。首夜盲刀2号试试水。","playerId":2,"playerName":"Claude","visibility":"camp","metadata":{},"timestamp":1776790919880},{"id":12,"type":"phase_start","content":"狼人投票","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"phase":"night_werewolf_vote","phaseName":"狼人投票","timestamp":1776790919881},{"id":13,"type":"wolf_vote_result","content":"狼人选择击杀 2号阿伟","playerId":8,"visibility":"camp","metadata":{},"voteDetails":[{"voter":"5号大军","target":"2号阿伟"},{"voter":"8号阿明","target":"2号阿伟"},{"voter":"9号aa","target":"2号阿伟"},{"voter":"12号Claude","target":"2号阿伟"}],"voteCounts":{"12":4},"timestamp":1776790943048},{"id":14,"type":"phase_start","content":"女巫技能","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"phase":"witch","phaseName":"女巫技能","timestamp":1776790943049},{"id":15,"type":"phase_start","content":"预言家查验","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"phase":"seer","phaseName":"预言家查验","timestamp":1776790945152},{"id":17,"type":"phase_start","content":"警长竞选","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"phase":"sheriff_campaign","phaseName":"警长竞选","timestamp":1776790952146},{"id":18,"type":"sheriff_candidates","content":"警上：1号阿华、5号大军、7号小娟、11号大刚 | 警下：2号阿伟、3号小云、4号阿鹏、6号小芳、8号阿明、9号aa、10号阿杰、12号Claude","visibility":"public","metadata":{"onStage":[{"id":7,"name":"阿华"},{"id":8,"name":"大军"},{"id":9,"name":"小娟"},{"id":4,"name":"大刚"}],"offStage