type":"phase_start","content":"狼人讨论","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"phase":"night_werewolf_discuss","phaseName":"狼人讨论","timestamp":1776790774252},{"id":8,"type":"speech","content":"首夜盲刀，大家随便聊聊目标。我建议从2、3、4里面选一个刀，看看能不能摸到神。大家觉得呢？","playerId":8,"playerName":"大军","visibility":"camp","metadata":{},"timestamp":1776790785560},{"id":9,"type":"speech","content":"同意5号，首夜没信息就盲刀2、3、4吧。我倾向于刀3号，中间位置容易出神。刀完看明天谁跳预言家再定策略。谁准备上警悍跳？","playerId":5,"playerName":"阿明","visibility":"camp","metadata":{},"timestamp":1776790788600},{"id":10,"type":"speech","content":"让5号憾跳吧，我们在警下，就2吧","playerId":1,"playerName":"aa","visibility":"camp","metadata":{},"timestamp":1776790889530},{"id":11,"type":"speech","content":"同意9号，5号上警悍跳，我警下观察。首夜盲刀2号试试水。","playerId":2,"playerName":"Claude","visibility":"camp","metadata":{},"timestamp":1776790919880},{"id":12,"type":"phase_start","content":"狼人投票","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"phase":"night_werewolf_vote","phaseName":"狼人投票","timestamp":1776790919881},{"id":13,"type":"wolf_vote_result","content":"狼人选择击杀 2号阿伟","playerId":8,"visibility":"camp","metadata":{},"voteDetails":[{"voter":"5号大军","target":"2号阿伟"},{"voter":"8号阿明","target":"2号阿伟"},{"voter":"9号aa","target":"2号阿伟"},{"voter":"12号Claude","target":"2号阿伟"}],"voteCounts":{"12":4},"timestamp":1776790943048},{"id":14,"type":"phase_start","content":"女巫技能","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"phase":"witch","phaseName":"女巫技能","timestamp":1776790943049},{"id":15,"type":"phase_start","content":"预言家查验","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"phase":"seer","phaseName":"预言家查验","timestamp":1776790945152},{"id":17,"type":"phase_start","content":"警长竞选","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"phase":"sheriff_campaign","phaseName":"警长竞选","timestamp":1776790952146},{"id":18,"type":"sheriff_candidates","content":"警上：1号阿华、5号大军、7号小娟、11号大刚 | 警下：2号阿伟、3号小云、4号阿鹏、6号小芳、8号阿明、9号aa、10号阿杰、12号Claude","visibility":"public","metadata":{"onStage":[{"id":7,"name":"阿华"},{"id":8,"name":"大军"},{"id":9,"name":"小娟"},{"id":4,"name":"大刚"}],"offStage":[{"id":12,"name":"阿伟"},{"id":6,"name":"小云"},{"id":3,"name":"阿鹏"},{"id":10,"name":"小芳"},{"id":5,"name":"阿明"},{"id":1,"name":"aa"},{"id":11,"name":"阿杰"},{"id":2,"name":"Claude"}]},"timestamp":1776790968357},{"id":19,"type":"phase_start","content":"警长竞选发言","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"phase":"sheriff_speech","phaseName":"警长竞选发言","timestamp":1776790968360},{"id":20,"type":"speech","content":"我是1号阿华，上警是为了拿警长带队。作为村民，我没有信息包袱，能客观分析发言和票型。我会用理性推理找狼，警徽也不会乱飞。选我，好人方向更清晰。","playerId":7,"playerName":"阿华","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"timestamp":1776790976323},{"id":21,"type":"speech","content":"我是真预言家！昨夜验6号小芳，金水。1号平民拿警徽毫无意义，信息权必须在真预言家手里。警徽流先7后11。6号及警下好人们，请把票投给我，我带队抓狼！","playerId":8,"playerName":"大军","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"timestamp":1776791006549},{"id":22,"type":"speech","content":"5号给我警徽流，我是好人验我必金水。1号村民抢警徽毫无意义！我上警本为诈身份，既然5号起跳，我7号村民退水，把舞台留给预言家。警下听11号和后置位发言。","playerId":9,"playerName":"小娟","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"timestamp":1776791028210},{"id":23,"type":"speech","content":"5号查验我，我是村民，验我必金水。1号平民抢警徽毫无意义，7号已退水。警徽必须给预言家带队，我也退水，不占警上位置。警下好人请投5号，我绝不拿警徽！","playerId":4,"playerName":"大刚","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"timestamp":1776791055464},{"id":24,"type":"system","content":"7号小娟 退水","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"timestamp":1776791059438},{"id":25,"type":"system","content":"11号大刚 退水","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"timestamp":1776791060210},{"id":26,"type":"system","content":"1号阿华 退水","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"timestamp":1776791070393},{"id":27,"type":"phase_start","content":"警长投票","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"phase":"sheriff_vote","phaseName":"警长投票","timestamp":1776791070395},{"id":28,"type":"sheriff_elected","content":"5号大军 当选警长","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"timestamp":1776791070396},{"id":29,"type":"phase_start","content":"公布死讯","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"phase":"day_announce","phaseName":"公布死讯","timestamp":1776791070399},{"id":30,"type":"last_words","content":"我是2号女巫阿伟！首夜狼刀信息我带走了，未能自救。5号预言家身份大概率可信，6号金水可认。毒药未用，后续女巫视角缺失，请守卫暗保神职。好人跟5号警长走，仔细分辨警徽流7、11的验人结果！","playerId":12,"playerName":"阿伟","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"timestamp":1776791093179},{"id":31,"type":"death_announce","content":"2号阿伟 死亡","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"deaths":[{"id":12,"name":"阿伟","reason":"wolf"}],"timestamp":1776791093180},{"id":32,"type":"phase_start","content":"白天讨论","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"phase":"day_discuss","phaseName":"白天讨论","timestamp":1776791093183},{"id":33,"type":"system","content":"警长指定从 3号小云 开始发言","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"timestamp":1776791120112},{"id":34,"type":"speech","content":"3号好人。2号女巫遗言认5号预言家，无人对跳，5号大概率真预，6号金水认下。警徽流7、11，听他俩发言。女巫已走，守卫注意保护神职。我跟5号警长走。","playerId":6,"playerName":"小云","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"timestamp":1776791132384},{"id":35,"type":"speech","content":"4号好人。2号女巫认下5号，5号单预言家，6号金水无疑。警徽流7、11，重点听他俩发言。我跟警长5号走，过。","playerId":3,"playerName":"阿鹏","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"timestamp":1776791139372},{"id":36,"type":"speech","content":"6号金水。5号单预言家，2号女巫认下，5号真预无疑。感谢5号验我，我认下这个身份。警徽流7、11，听他俩发言分辨。女巫已走，好人抱紧5号警长，我跟5号走。","playerId":10,"playerName":"小芳","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"timestamp":1776791152144},{"id":37,"type":"speech","content":"7号村民。5号单预2号女巫认，6号金水无疑，我警上退水已表水，验我必金水。重点点1号，警上平民抢警徽毫无逻辑，大概率狼。认5号，过。","playerId":9,"playerName":"小娟","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"timestamp":1776791166022},{"id":38,"type":"speech","content":"8号好人。2号女巫认下5号，5号真预无疑，6号金水。1号警上村民抢警徽毫无逻辑，像狼抢警徽，重点关注。7号退水表水还行。守卫今晚必保5号警长，好人紧跟5号走，过。","playerId":5,"playerName":"阿明","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"timestamp":1776791187939},{"id":39,"type":"speech","content":"2号如果是真女巫的话，为什么守夜不自救？她必然自救啊，要么就是守卫也守了她。同守同救死了？","playerId":1,"playerName":"aa","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"timestamp":1776791276896},{"id":40,"type":"speech","content":"9号质疑合理，2号若真女巫首夜不自救确实反常。但5号单预言家无人对跳，若2号假女巫，真女巫应择机起跳澄清。暂认5号，保持警惕。","playerId":11,"playerName":"阿杰","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"timestamp":1776791289437},{"id":41,"type":